sequenceDiagram
    participant GS as Game server (proveedor)
    participant LN as Luna Negra API
    participant N as Relays Nostr
    participant P as Jugador (modal)
    participant W as Alby Hub / NWC
    participant T as Tick (QStash)

    GS->>LN: POST /escrow/bets (firmado NIP-98)
    LN->>LN: verifica pubkey == dueño del game
    LN->>N: publica contrato (tag a npubs) [inmutable]
    LN-->>GS: 201 { betId, depositDeadline (+10m) }
    P->>LN: POST /escrow/bets/{id}/deposit (Bearer)
    LN->>W: makeInvoice (msat)
    LN-->>P: 200 { invoice, QR }
    P->>W: paga el invoice
    loop cada ~1 min
        T->>LN: POST /escrow/tick (firma QStash)
        LN->>W: lookupInvoice (pendientes)
        alt todos depositaron
            LN->>LN: status = ready, resolveDeadline +15m
        else venció 10m incompleto
            LN->>W: payInvoice reembolso (idempotente)
            LN->>LN: status = cancelled_incomplete
        end
    end
